sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client<br/>(OpenAI-compatible)
    participant Gateway as vllm-orchestrator-gateway<br/>8090/TCP HTTP
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8085/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Detectors as Guardrails Detectors<br/>(e.g., regex-detector)
    participant LLM as vLLM / LLM Server

    Note over Gateway: Startup: loads YAML config<br/>creates route per detector pipeline

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,LLM: Flow 1: Chat Completion with Detector Filtering
        Client->>Gateway: POST /{route_name}/v1/chat/completions<br/>Authorization: Bearer <token><br/>Content-Type: application/json
        Note over Gateway: Injects route's detector config<br/>into request payload
        Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Authorization: <forwarded><br/>X-Forwarded-*: <forwarded><br/>Optional mTLS
        Orchestrator->>Detectors: Run input detectors<br/>(per detector config)
        Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results (input)
        Orchestrator->>LLM: Forward generation request
        LLM-->>Orchestrator: Generated completion
        Orchestrator->>Detectors: Run output detectors<br/>(per detector config)
        Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results (output)
        Orchestrator-->>Gateway: Response with completions<br/>+ detections field
        Note over Gateway: No detections found:<br/>forwards response as-is
        Gateway-->>Client: 200 OK<br/>OpenAI-compatible JSON response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 235, 235)
        Note over Client,LLM: Flow 2: Detection Triggered (Fallback Response)
        Client->>Gateway: POST /{route_name}/v1/chat/completions<br/>Authorization: Bearer <token>
        Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>+ injected detector config<br/>Optional mTLS
        Orchestrator->>Detectors: Run detectors
        Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detections found!
        Orchestrator-->>Gateway: Response with populated<br/>detections field
        Note over Gateway: Detections found +<br/>fallback_message configured:<br/>replaces choices[0].message.content
        Gateway-->>Client: 200 OK<br/>Fallback message in response
    end
